title: SCP-9999 Placeholder
content:
Due to [https://05command.wikidot.com/forum/t-17033247/scp-9999-slot-reservation#post-6814059 the vote held here], the SCP-9999 slot is to be placeholdered indefinitely until the Contest Team decides it is suitable to release it.

This slot will not be available in the upcoming SCP-9000 contest.
author: Naepic
